Runs inside JupyterLab
Opens and edits Drawio XML created on diagrams.net, Confluence, etc.
Import/export to editable XML, PNG, SVG & Notebook with live preview
Exports print-ready PDF with optional embedded editable XML (requires serverextension)
Basic drag-drop content reuse with notebooks
All drawio plugins, like flow, explore and SQL
All drawio shapes, even offline
Fully customizable via Lab Advanced Settings
